				\begin{document}$${{{\bar{\mathrm d}}}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M6"><mml:mover accent="true"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="normal">d</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>¯</mml:mo></mml:mover></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="41540_2022_241_Article_IEq2.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the mean pairwise distance and n<sub>mm</sub> is the number of mismatches.</p>
      <p id="Par18">Equation 2 (aggregate score):<disp-formula id="Equ2"><label>2</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M7">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
